{"tid":1530233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一次軍事鎮壓會變成國際醜聞，無數次的警察打人卻可以推定無罪。","createTime":"2019-09-02T01:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T02:05:29.000Z","uid":79965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8085b98615fe171d3113518c72e9884c763d7675","tid":1530233,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:51:49.000Z","msg":"//一次軍事鎮壓會變成國際醜聞，無數次的警察打人卻可以推定無罪。那些警察全副武裝卻沒有身份，打死人不償命的。他們以分期付款的方式，一週幾次，在入夜的暗巷裡，大街上，地鐵站，關不起來的車門車廂裡，一棍一棍，一罐一罐，一槍一槍，提領示威者的命，把小孩當大人打，把大人當小孩打，打得你半死，半死而不全死，並不是什麼手下留情賞你半條命，而是因為，骯髒戰爭的詭計在於：只要看起來沒有殺人，就可以繼續殺。//<br />\n<br />\n轉載自fb<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n所以連登仔一定好快諗到，<br />\n平時遍地開花無問題，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但短期內我地需要大規模活動。</span></span>所以唔需要站站塞鐵。會唔會有站內示威？集中係2，3個站。可以係附近站上車，然後同一時間係某站落車。返工放工時間，係地鐵站內大規模示威，唔知香港市民今次睇唔睇到？<br />\n<br />\n我好驚，大家唔好亂黎呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749d237b4e38e0c0c0d99dba81b1bb945ffcd2e7","tid":1530233,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:59:00.000Z","msg":"港鐵禁制令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda34c91ae914d7d879d6c9263eb39c17a19bb54","tid":1530233,"uid":31094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:59:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/journodannyaero/status/1167994686591496192?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjournodannyaero%2Fstatus%2F1167994686591496192%3Fs%3D21&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=2a3a2b52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjournodannyaero%2Fstatus%2F1167994686591496192%3Fs%3D21&h=ce8b256b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/journodannyaero/status/1167994686591496192?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n山長水遠跑嚟咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ef5600e164a0b770eda3f778a2b07fa4bff992","tid":1530233,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:03:34.000Z","msg":"無架喎，懲罰黨鐵係必然，連登仔連集體係黨鐵商舖玩都唔敢？你呃我呀"},{"pid":"29bb7bc25ae72dde5f5b3398026dba04a7b7eb16","tid":1530233,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:05:29.000Z","msg":"清算警隊, 軍隊, 從來都係要新政府去做<br />\n即係要林奠下台, 新特首先可以清算班狗"}]}